GreenBang - Alpine Linux Live ISO Distribution

GreenBang is an Alpine Linux based live ISO distribution inspired by CrunchBang Linux.
It features a minimal, keyboard-driven Wayland desktop environment built on:
- labwc (Wayland compositor)
- waybar (status bar)
- foot (terminal)
- rofi-wayland (application launcher)
- NetworkManager (network management)

For more information, visit: https://greenbang.org

